<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>11</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Abraham Pathien, Isak Pathien, Jakob Pathien,
 Alpha leh Omega, Abul leh Tawp!
 Israelte A puidawk a gamgaw gam ah,
 Mana'n A vak hi;
 Jordan gallam a kaitau ui, Kanaan gam ah,
 Pathien umpihna maktak mai a nei ui.

[V2]
 Na umna chu (2) kipak a um,
 Na umna ah (2) lamdanna mak a nei ui.

[V3]
 2. Kei gilo a, liengvai leh hansie puo chung ahin,
 A thamuonna maktak a hungtung tai;
 Tuipi bang in ei chup kimvel, ka gen thiem puoi,
 A hehpihna le;
 Sapman um leh ngaihman um ka paupih Lalpa,
 A hehpihna chawian ing ka, Hosanna!

[V4]
 A hehpihna (2) a makna e!
 A hehpihna (2) chawian ing ka, Hosanna!

[V5]
 3. Thepna huihpi a nung mihiem theihna khel lam ah,
 Guol ding neilo in thihna luiguom ah;
 Ei tuomvel ie, beidawna leh lungzinnate'n,
 Ei hukdawk ding in,
 Bethlehem leh Kalvari tang chu hawhpai in,
 Zopa lopi, Lal Isu'n ei hukdawkta'i!

[V6]
 Ka mamawh haw (2) A neikim a,
 Ka mamawh haw (2) Amah ah kana muta'i.

[V7]
 4. Muol a liem zotai ka etchimloh leh ka hehpih,
 Ka kapkap hi, lungawihna neilo in;
 Thihna Jordan ei kaihsan tai, lunglam ka vai,
 Heilo pak chawi in!
 Thamuonna mak ka gen sengpuoi, aw Lal Isu'n,
 &quot;Hehpihna ziek chauh ahi,&quot; tih ei hilh hi.

[V8]
 Thamuonna mak (2) ka gen thiempuo'i,
 Thamuonna mak (2) Lalpa ah ka na mutai.</lyrics>
<title>GOD IS WITH US</title>
</song>